    <item>
      <title>Rigorous numerics of invariant manifolds</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/event/summer-meeting/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Jan 2019 13:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/event/summer-meeting/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This presentation discusses rigorous numerical methods for studying invariant manifolds in dynamical systems. The talk explores computational approaches that provide mathematically rigorous results about the structure and properties of invariant manifolds in differential equations. The presentation highlights the importance of these techniques for understanding the global behavior of nonlinear dynamical systems.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
